This #WorldHealthDay, let's raise our voices for:

#HealthEquity 👩🏾‍⚕️
Health care for ALL 🌎
#Vaccine access 💉

.1% of #COVID19 vaccine doses have been administered in low-income countries. This needs to change - all countries & communities deserve access.
